DSym_SongPos  (&4588C)
#Parent DSym_
=>	R0 =	-1 to read sequence pos
		other, to set
	R1 =	-1 to read pattern pos
		other, to set

<=	R0 =	previous sequence pos
	R1 =	previous pattern pos (0-63)

This call reads or sets the pattern position in song and the note position in pattern. If the pattern position is changed, the current note is reset to 0.